# Tooling Stack Context

- The application must use ESM modules only.
- Do not use CommonJS (CJS) module format.
- Use Vite for build workflows.
- Use Vitest for unit and integration testing by default.
- Use Cucumber only when a feature explicitly requires BDD functional scenarios.
- Use BiomeJS for linting and formatting.
- Use NestJS to build API applications.
- Use OpenTelemetry for metrics, traces, and observability instrumentation.
